SUMMARY:Easter Brunch at Casa Loma
DESCRIPTION:Experience the splendor of Casa Loma this Easter Sunday. Our annual Brunch\, served in the stately elegance of Toronto’s famous castle\, is an event your family will long remember. After brunch\, explore the castle at your leisure. Guests with a later seating time are welcome to arrive early and tour the Castle before their reservation\, as the Castle closes at 5 pm. \n$90 per person plus applicable taxes$65 per child (4-13 years old) plus applicable taxes \nAdmission to tour Casa Loma is included. \nTo make your reservation\, click here. \nAn advanced payment is required to confirm your reservation. To contact the reservations team\, please email reservations@casaloma.ca
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/easter-brunch-at-casa-loma/
LOCATION:Casa Loma\, 1 Austin Terrace\, Toronto\, M5R 1X8
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/easter-brunch-at-casa-loma.png
END:VEVENT
