SUMMARY:Easter Rose Garden Bouquet Workshop - Reid's Distillery x Lou-Lou
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate spring with a hands-on\, Easter rose garden-inspired bouquet workshop while enjoying the exclusive launch of Reid’s Distillery new RTD Cucumber Rose Collins. \nYour Ticket Includes:• 1.5 hours of guided floral bouquet-making workshop led by Lou-Lou’s Flowers• All flowers and materials• A finished bouquet to take home• 1 Cucumber Rose Collins RTD to enjoy during your experience! \nNo experience needed. Just bring your creativity. \nPerfect for Easter weekend plans\, date night\, or a spring reset. \nReserve your spot and sip into the season. 🌸
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/easter-rose-garden-bouquet-workshop-reids-distillery-x-lou-lou/
LOCATION:Reid’s Distillery Lounge\, 32 Logan Ave\, Toronto\, M4M 2M8
CATEGORIES:Classes & Workshops,Community Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/easter-rose-garden-bouquet-workshop-reids-distillery-x-lou-lou.png
