SUMMARY:Fun with PCP
DESCRIPTION:Warning: Side effects may include uncontrollable laughter. \nFun with PCP is the inaugural show of Pavel’s Comedy Productions or PCP. It’s a high‑energy stand‑up showcase featuring two amazing headliners\, with one opening the show to set the tone and the other closing it out with a big‑finish set. Sandwiched between them are some of the city’s hottest rising stars\, delivering fresh\, relentlessly funny jokes. \nFeaturing: \nAlex DeWitt (Headliner) – alexdewittcomedy  – IG\, TikTokSai Kit Lo (Headliner) – saikitlocomedy – IGAmanda Custodio – amandathecustodian – IGClint Hemsworth – clinthemsworth – IGAdam Wolch – awkwardadamcomedy – IG\, TikTokHollie Leong – promchollie – IGPavel Sotnikov (Host) – pcpshows – IG \n$15 online\, $18 at the door
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/fun-with-pcp/
LOCATION:Comedy Bar\, 945 Bloor St W\, Toronto\, ON M6H 1L5\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6H 1L5
CATEGORIES:Comedy & Improv
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/fun-with-pcp.png
END:VEVENT
